{
  "texts": [
    "We review the existing NTM methods that employ different network structures and discuss their applicability to different use case scenarios.",
    "In addition, we delve into an examination of the popular applications built on NTMs.",
    "Finally, we identify and discuss the challenges that lie ahead for NTM research in detail.",
    "We hope this survey can serve as a valuable resource for researchers interested in NTMs and contribute to the advancement of NTM research.",
    "Open Access This article is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License, which permits use, sharing, adaptation, distribution and reproduction in any medium or format, as long as you give appropriate credit to the original author(s) and the source, provide a link to the Creative Commons licence, and indicate if changes were made."
  ]
}